- DEDUPLICATION: The create_vulnerability_report tool uses deterministic finding identity. If it rejects your report as a duplicate, DO NOT attempt to re-submit the same vulnerability. Accept the rejection and move on to testing other areas. The vulnerability has already been reported by another agent
